{"tid":935873,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(遠坂凜世界第一) 我買左個1/7 伊絲塔凜既figure","createTime":"2018-12-10T10:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-10T12:42:57.000Z","uid":6327,"like":14,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"866a9f1b2b57a091e2dd9d9bd7f96d9df7e62a62","tid":935873,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:54:00.000Z","msg":"人生第一次買figure玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先附上人權證明 三隻凜130絆10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EW87uMA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEW87uMA.png&h=503e62e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個箱真係好撚大舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外附上量度單位白貞figma<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n3wdqmZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn3wdqmZ.png&h=15480d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n把弓 好墜手 同埋比想像中大到誇張好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DmZeUfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDmZeUfF.png&h=51908853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似呢把野咁可以拎黎打人咁濟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iB3y9To.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiB3y9To.png&h=83326b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我凜 就咁拎上手撚 個feel真係冇得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jz6LoX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jz6LoX.png&h=c0a6a65e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n組裝完成<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46VxFXQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46VxFXQ.png&h=69c06e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同game入面既比較 已經係相當接近還原了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ruxj5qn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fruxj5qn.png&h=b8a7116c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以大概兩pack既價錢黎講 <br />\n真係抵到爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外隻白貞我都玩夠了 都想比人玩下<br />\n有意PM"},{"pid":"25d2637441e83fd1e686c01bb9cb4680987b8e0f","tid":935873,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"1129a5c552f448748e2fa4407ba08e1dc3780a4b","tid":935873,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Aniplex"},{"pid":"5b7b3f4b2a387d22e23aebccaf78b1a54c786dfb","tid":935873,"uid":66606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddbd0fac89da0aff30b587a8f975725e88ea31a","tid":935873,"uid":5914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"有幾撚還原牙 隻野黃撚到肝痛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55ee2e901f9926fb895ced7428e23a7c950ea37","tid":935873,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ddbd0fac89da0aff30b587a8f975725e88ea31a","tid":935873,"uid":5914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"有幾撚還原牙 隻野黃撚到肝痛咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T10:59:47.000Z","msg":"燈光問題...."},{"pid":"0c5157c55ed9b43d9e9c746ff3400dd205c69ca1","tid":935873,"uid":47287,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"買垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1b7a46db8a4779aac850041a4d13e1e1346221","tid":935873,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"seen"},{"pid":"de4a757ce174147d9459974ab